Title: Blow
Plot: Earl takes on number 101 on his list, "Stole a girl's identity."  The girl turns out to be Joy's half-sister that she never knew about and the one person that could possibly help her get sympathy from the jury.  The problem, Joy and Liberty are enemies.
GuestStars: DJ Qualls,  Tamala Jones,  Sam Menning,  M. Darnell Suttles,  Kelli Goss,  Jon Hughes,  Brooklin Yearwood,  Bess Fanning,  Arreale Davis,  Marnie Crossen,  Jonathan Slavin,  Dale Dickey,  Gigi Goff
